Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise... Kurisu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I did knock, for what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you discern our location!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Mr. Hashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He called it a "laboratory,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was expecting something a little more grand than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru, did you betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You were deceived by the wiles of a 3D woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you! Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just consider him confused by certain current events.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Organization has finally sent an agent of theirs to the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is this, too, the choice of Steins;Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Steins;Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Okarin made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mixing up his German and English.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in America for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese men don't know how to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're freaking out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I can feel murderous intent seeping from your every pore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they call the "martial arts"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I came here to see if your claim that I'd been stabbed was real,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or just an excuse for sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems something more important has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no damage to the stalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She may attempt to trigger some sort of explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let her out of your sight for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any tweezers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mushy inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're hungry, say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd eat a pervert's banana, anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You poked at me, attempting to touch me out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Makise? Miss Makise? {Suffix is makise-shi which no one will know}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you say, "Who'd eat a pervert's banana, anyways?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,once more, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, with an upset expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset? {not a ? ???}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you imagine something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with it, genius girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear what the genius imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you're both perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say the person with the perverted imagination is the pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You perverted genius girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we're at the point where
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could sue you for sexual harassment right this minute, but I'll let it slide for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, tell me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This banana has something to do with that microwave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Gadget #8, the Phone Microwave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is my lab's secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss Makise might be able to explain how this strange device works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to understand, we'll never figure this out on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the Future Gadget Lab's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cristina, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the secrets of the Phone Microwave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but on two conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One, you must become a member of the Future Gadget Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to join your lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm returning to America in August...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be just until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about any acts of sexual harassment I've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, you're a petty person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A very petty person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love that. Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the conditions are very favorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorable to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making my brain send out too much norepinephrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Cristina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "-tina"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, "The Zombie."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it right, Hououin Pervert-Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Perverted Genius Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perverts glaring at one another... Win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no more "Pervert."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop calling you one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, from now on, you're Lab Member 004!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cristina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No "-tina"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Juicy Karaage Number One... Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's a teleporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing else,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't teleport the single banana or the banana bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for just showing up out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiina Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm a lab member now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A lab member?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A female lab member!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first female lab member since Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an electrical discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of lightning shot out from the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, around noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the alert about the satellite crash and ran out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I connected my phone to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when I sent that message,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your phone was hooked up to the Phone Microwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The one about Miss Makise being stabbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a week ago, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't it here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When this happened, what was the microwave doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was running a systems test...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think it was during the reverse spin testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should try to recreate the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri, bring me the Juicy Karaage Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give each of you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we need to put something in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens to its contents when it rotates backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistant, send a message to my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did I become your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know your number anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru, your phone's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What should the subject be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cristina is a pervert."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that's off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll split the difference and go with "Okarin is a pervert"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hashida, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we wait for the message to reach the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's ready now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta turn on the fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The EM waves, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A microwave's EM waves couldn't split a desk just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all black!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just bought them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do about the hole in the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Braun finds that, we'll be in serious trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,7/24, 17:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It went back to the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's all coming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The one answer this all points to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The banana, split off from the bunch, returned to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The message traveled five days into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Phone Microwave is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...a time machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I dubbed her the "Shining Finger."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But this many?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Message me now."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you asleep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"How long are you going to sleep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage is pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked all night, with nothing to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they turning into gel-banas anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only time we were able to send a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we call Miss Makise back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(438,1)}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The LHC.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Large Hadron Collider,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,SERN's particle accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels nice, just looking at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,SERN maintains an exclusive monopoly on time machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,John Titor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the one you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,@channel can't get enough of the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Titor was explaining that they completed a time machine by 2034!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the acronym for the European Organization in Nuclear Research and Particle Physics. {D: NB - used onscreen name shown in about 2 seconds, thus changed the "for" to "in"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Its H.Q. is just outside Geneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As the name suggests, its main work is in particle physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has some of the world's best facilities for it:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Low Energy Antiproton Ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Proton Synchrotron Booster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the Large Electron–Positron Collider...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the last boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's biggest particle accelerator,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Large Hadron Collider~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There were rumors that the LHC could generate a miniature black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A black hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't one proposed time travel method
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,utilize a miniature black hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you attended Miss Makise's lecture, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She said creating a black hole was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the LHC exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,SERN's publicly denied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say, "where there's smoke, there's fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,El Psy Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, exactly, are you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing for us to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Faris'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a supah hakah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should smile smugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "hacker," not "hakah," all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hack into SERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin... This is a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to find out what evil they're up to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and find hints about the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether we make the Phone Microwave into a real time machine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or let it rest forever in the lab storeroom is up to your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me for whatever happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two orders of beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,800 yen total.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Slacking off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the shop's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more of a bicycle shop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, what are you guys doing on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Gadget Lab, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you learn that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that much, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting against an organization
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that rules the world from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, we're hacking into that organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is SERN that organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I overheard you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were spying on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at keeping my mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A message that someone died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's obsessed with some old PC
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,called an IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,An IBN?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I saw it on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that guy who claimed to be a time traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,John Titor, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on @channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The IBN 5100 was built before the widespread use of the BASIC language,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can read IBN's proprietary programming language or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the Titor who appeared in 2000 also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You all seem to have fixed ideas about the nature of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Time isn't a single line, moving from past to future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I were to go back in time and kill someone we'll call "A."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This alters something called the divergence number,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world line moves to a world without A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's a world line shift, people's memories are altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, memories of the world line where A existed are deleted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and replaced with memories of a world line where A doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(560,1)}I'm more interested in how SERN,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a research organization, ends up as the planetary ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a question I've been asking for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe what SERN says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already succeeded in \Ncreating a miniature black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be easiest to describe a dystopia as the revival of communism,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world's reversion to the 18th century's living standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By 2036, SERN holds most of the world's science and technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you need the IBN 5100 to change this future?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the IBN 5100's abilities to stop their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The John Titor who appeared in 2000 said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The "me" who appeared ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've said, I've unfortunately never been to the year 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's possible you saw me in a different world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my address.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you contact me, I'll answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've almost got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can just access the SQL table list, figuring out the password should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been up two nights in a row, so I brought snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Canned fishcake stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me another sometime, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii doesn't have enough pocket money to treat you too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to buy my Rai-Net sausage, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Upa again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to enjoy this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some for Daru and Kurisu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not listening at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him to take a break, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His supah hakah's soul is burning bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say "hakah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not good to nose around in the secrets of others, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to reveal SERN's plots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kurisu left because she was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that had nothing to do with the hacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant ran off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trade you a mandarin for a beef strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have a quail egg, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I like quail eggs almost as much as I like beef strips.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii likes quail eggs too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give you a fish sausage instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I like fish sausages more than mandarins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then negotiations have concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here's my beef strip...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! I got it! I got it! I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give up, and show me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ID get!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand, but wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the hacking's complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are limits to what I can see without being an admin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I can only see the boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naughty, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, just some e-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,English?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get Dr. Excite in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, that's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "Hi, Paul!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need your acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"The LHC is working well."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's as fickle as a cat, but for the past month,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"...it's been working surprisingly well."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, does anything here mention a time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The phrase "time machine" doesn't show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the last month, the word "Z-program" has been used over a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Z-Program Experiment Report 137."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"The miniature black hole mission has already been established,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"...so I'll skip that report."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miniature black hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They announced publically that those experiments were a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What else does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Experiment result..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Human is dead,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"...mismatch."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Human is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...died.
